Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.40,0:01:39.40,jinggao,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\be1\an8}翻譯：萝卜子；校對：千葉命；歌詞：七海·拓；\N後期：消失的风使；繁化：黑羽侖人。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.49,0:01:43.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唔…選哪個好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.07,0:01:45.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說你是要給誰
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.02,0:01:47.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和朋友們一起吃
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.91,0:01:50.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然…我就猜是那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.30,0:01:54.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女孩子之間互相交換巧克力也很有趣哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.59,0:01:59.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿茲特克文明  咖啡因  可可
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.69,0:02:07.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.20,0:02:09.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？怎麼了  千秋
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.29,0:02:12.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也教教我怎麼做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.77,0:02:15.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  好啊  夏奈你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.33,0:02:21.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  我就算了  情人節跟我沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.43,0:02:25.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你反正會用天生的貪婪的性格
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.55,0:02:28.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從那些受歡迎的男生手裡搶巧克力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.59,0:02:30.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦…哦——
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.50,0:02:31.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.67,0:02:32.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.19,0:02:37.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對啊！可以吃個夠啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.38,0:02:41.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說…這可不是在給你提什麼好建議
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.44,0:02:45.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,機會難得  夏奈也一起做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.67,0:02:48.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉～我就算了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.24,0:02:52.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,送禮不如收禮
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.48,0:02:55.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行哦  這可是女孩子的慶典呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.86,0:02:57.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧  千秋
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.27,0:02:58.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉？嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.87,0:03:01.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以夏奈也要一起做  好不好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.88,0:03:05.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慶典…節日  節日！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.34,0:03:11.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要反擊了！睡衣派對上春香的招待實在太搶眼了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.39,0:03:15.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不會又想什麼歪點子吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.32,0:03:18.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  把大家都叫來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.76,0:03:20.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,召開情人節慶典！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.76,0:03:22.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂…喂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.89,0:03:27.89,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}第7碗  越嚼越甜哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.61,0:03:34.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位  都準備好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.22,0:03:36.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.01,0:03:41.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼我要穿成這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.07,0:03:43.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什麼呀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.49,0:03:46.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是阿珍  是女孩子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.31,0:03:48.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情人節是女孩子的慶典
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.52,0:03:50.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不參加怎麼行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.90,0:03:52.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過…可是我…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.69,0:03:55.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦？你想說自己不是女的？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.64,0:03:57.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咱們的友情還真是短暫啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.45,0:04:02.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等…等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.13,0:04:03.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.23,0:04:08.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的意思是…以後不准出入這裡了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.85,0:04:18.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧  我做就是了  我會努力幫忙的！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.63,0:04:29.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香姐  我能幫什麼忙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.01,0:04:31.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想做什麼樣的巧克力呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.81,0:04:35.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個…啊  可愛點的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.86,0:04:37.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  那麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.29,0:04:40.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先把巧克力分成小塊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.26,0:04:43.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後我會把它切得更碎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.21,0:04:44.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.31,0:04:50.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說  為什麼我要來這兒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.10,0:04:52.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為是節日嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.68,0:04:54.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.18,0:04:57.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不打算送給誰嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.53,0:04:58.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巧克力？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.54,0:05:00.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會送啦  那種東西…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.73,0:05:02.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是有哥哥嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.96,0:05:05.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給哥哥？怎麼可能…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.32,0:05:08.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛  真是個孤僻的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.02,0:05:11.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我很孤僻嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.51,0:05:16.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.44,0:05:20.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  等你很久了  快點兒進來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.64,0:05:21.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.42,0:05:23.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  歡迎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.32,0:05:25.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還真熱鬧啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.19,0:05:34.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…很孤僻嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.77,0:05:40.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還順利嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.55,0:05:42.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？還行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.33,0:05:45.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋你要送給誰
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.25,0:05:49.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,內田要把巧克力送給誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.63,0:05:52.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  完全沒想過呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.75,0:05:54.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是個沒計劃的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.52,0:06:02.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉野  你要把巧克力送給誰
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.10,0:06:05.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給爸爸  昨天做好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.63,0:06:08.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛  一群無聊的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.98,0:06:11.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說夏奈你要送誰
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.35,0:06:13.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只負責收
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.70,0:06:24.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思啊  要你們兩個來幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.07,0:06:26.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事兒啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.91,0:06:29.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對啊  反正有空嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.18,0:06:31.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.60,0:06:33.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真礙事  給我出去！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.79,0:06:34.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.92,0:06:36.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小氣小氣小氣！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.87,0:06:39.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏奈還是一樣那麼有活力
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.88,0:06:40.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.56,0:06:43.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿珍要把巧克力送給誰
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.03,0:06:44.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.18,0:06:49.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春…春香姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.36,0:06:50.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不准
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.09,0:06:52.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…那個
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.05,0:06:54.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說不准
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.41,0:06:56.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋你真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.13,0:06:57.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.21,0:07:01.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過機會難得  送給男孩子怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.66,0:07:02.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.95,0:07:04.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有想送的人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.41,0:07:07.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有想送的人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.91,0:07:10.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔  原來有那樣的對象啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.10,0:07:13.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…這個
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.84,0:07:18.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿…阿真同學
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.74,0:07:19.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦——
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.98,0:07:23.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪  你見過阿真？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.42,0:07:26.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…那個…應該吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.73,0:07:29.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就直說了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.62,0:07:32.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是放棄他吧  他就是個智障兒童
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.86,0:07:34.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎麼會
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.56,0:07:39.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巧克力真是好吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.14,0:07:42.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣好嗎  這不是備用的巧克力嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.28,0:07:44.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係  沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.57,0:07:49.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.45,0:07:50.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.22,0:07:53.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我果真是個孤僻的人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.26,0:07:55.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？哲學性的問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.41,0:07:58.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.84,0:08:13.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.54,0:08:15.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題  沒問題的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.24,0:08:24.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.66,0:08:26.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  做得不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.62,0:08:29.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明不是我動手  可還是會緊張呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.29,0:08:31.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋  這才剛開始呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.18,0:08:38.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去哪兒啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.57,0:08:39.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,廁所
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.46,0:08:45.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪  怎麼就化不開呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.99,0:09:00.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,微火…超微火
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.76,0:09:03.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不錯啊  融化的巧克力也夠美味
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.34,0:09:05.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！做什麼呢你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.18,0:09:17.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏奈  你…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.06,0:09:19.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,試吃一下就光光了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.26,0:09:21.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我滾！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.20,0:09:27.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  做得不錯  就那樣繼續拌吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.00,0:09:31.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害啊  阿珍
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.24,0:09:34.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼擅長家事  你隨時都可以嫁人了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.38,0:09:38.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嫁人…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.70,0:09:40.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  什麼焦了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.21,0:09:43.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊！怎麼辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.89,0:09:45.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了來了  我這就來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.45,0:09:49.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿珍？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.41,0:09:58.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬馬  冬馬  快起來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.43,0:10:01.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹嘛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.97,0:10:03.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巧克力貌似不夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.07,0:10:04.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.14,0:10:07.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去買回來  馬上去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.60,0:10:08.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.58,0:10:09.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是吃了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.10,0:10:10.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.60,0:10:14.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還不趕緊去買  你這蠢貨
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.32,0:10:15.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.40,0:10:23.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.02,0:10:24.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.84,0:10:28.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏奈不也吃巧克力了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.12,0:10:30.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！冬馬
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.75,0:10:32.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  藤岡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.52,0:10:35.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼  買完東西回家？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.73,0:10:39.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…夏奈叫我去買巧克力啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.86,0:10:42.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦？南讓你買  為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.99,0:10:46.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…那個  因為讓我幫她做啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.59,0:10:51.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,需要男生幫忙嗎  那我也去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.27,0:10:52.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.84,0:10:53.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.55,0:10:57.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說…你看…可能是準備送給你的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.36,0:11:00.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定不願意被本人看到吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.00,0:11:05.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…走了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.15,0:11:11.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南給我…巧克力…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.32,0:11:17.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我買回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.45,0:11:19.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢死了  冬馬
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.42,0:11:22.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是你  讓我遭罪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.43,0:11:24.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.13,0:11:29.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等稍微凝固一下  就可以裝飾了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.78,0:11:43.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經凝固了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.41,0:11:44.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還早啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.75,0:11:46.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就說還早呢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.37,0:11:50.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之告一段落了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.42,0:11:51.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們來喝茶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.90,0:11:52.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了～
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.78,0:12:07.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬馬呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.01,0:12:11.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  好像買完東西就回家了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.44,0:12:13.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說是累了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.45,0:12:15.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她明明什麼都沒做
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.14,0:12:18.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿珍也回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.63,0:12:20.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒耐性的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.44,0:12:24.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我收到了阿珍的巧克力  真幸運
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.57,0:12:28.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到頭來還是沒給阿真  沒問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.02,0:12:30.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好喝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.54,0:12:32.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概明白他是白癡了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.40,0:12:39.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香  給我巧克力吃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.67,0:12:42.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  剩下那些你隨便吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.75,0:12:48.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要再來一杯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.12,0:12:51.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀呀  抱歉  沒問題吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.37,0:12:53.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.76,0:12:56.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來  千秋要送給誰
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.10,0:13:05.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  就是那傢伙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.91,0:13:07.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隔壁的冬木
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.38,0:13:08.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.27,0:13:08.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.16,0:13:10.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉～這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.24,0:13:13.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.39,0:13:14.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.72,0:13:16.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別害羞  別害羞
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.61,0:13:19.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在那兒胡說八道什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.68,0:13:23.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了好了  不管送誰  對方能高興就好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.77,0:13:26.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀哎呀  年輕真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.05,0:13:46.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好吃～
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.48,0:13:47.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗚…！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.60,0:13:55.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣  好吃吧  這可是為你特製的巧克力
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.87,0:13:59.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼淚都流出來啦  開心就好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.47,0:14:09.90,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(蠢貨)
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.14,0:14:14.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弄不好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.27,0:14:16.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  千秋  幫幫忙啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.19,0:14:19.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了  現在別煩我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.68,0:14:22.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.65,0:14:24.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦好啦  我來幫你啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.92,0:14:35.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…春香姐姐  抱歉…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.12,0:14:37.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那樣盯著我看…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.58,0:14:40.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  對不起  千秋  你慢慢做
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.63,0:14:41.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做好了！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.88,0:14:44.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做得很漂亮呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.63,0:14:45.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起來真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.66,0:14:47.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.58,0:14:51.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是有男生可以送就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.05,0:14:53.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明只是個小學生
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.16,0:14:55.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就開始搞這些你情我愛的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.49,0:14:58.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光吃不做的傢伙沒資格這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.75,0:15:02.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要接受對方  巧克力就毫無價值
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.69,0:15:05.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但也有人會因為這無價值的東西而感到幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.74,0:15:09.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情人節真是無可挑剔啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.26,0:15:17.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安  藤岡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.62,0:15:18.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  早安
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.96,0:15:27.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.40,0:15:30.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天一份人情巧克力也不能收
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.53,0:15:33.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要全都還回去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.82,0:15:36.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…是誰送的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.00,0:15:37.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤岡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.55,0:15:42.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早…早啊  南同學
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.74,0:15:45.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤岡  你是不是收了很多巧克力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.82,0:15:47.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個也沒有收到哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.04,0:15:48.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.35,0:15:55.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.59,0:15:59.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找個機會把巧克力送給藤岡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.85,0:16:01.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是能收下就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.16,0:16:07.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.04,0:16:10.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,防止別人送巧克力給藤岡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.20,0:16:16.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真礙事…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.20,0:16:20.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點讓開啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.41,0:16:24.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要站那兒多久啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.18,0:16:28.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有要送的跡象呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.72,0:16:35.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小倉鼠  你看～
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.84,0:16:37.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起來很好吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.84,0:16:42.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小倉鼠也想要巧克力嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.63,0:16:44.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.16,0:16:49.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊！我的巧克力…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.17,0:16:51.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別隨便喂它啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.31,0:16:57.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,送給你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.87,0:16:59.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬馬  收下巧克力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.89,0:17:00.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉？我？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.98,0:17:04.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  因為冬馬比男生還要帥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.40,0:17:05.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就算了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.07,0:17:08.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  也給我們一些啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.74,0:17:09.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來  接著
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.19,0:17:13.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉～
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.59,0:17:17.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這回你可是名副其實的男生了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.31,0:17:31.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香  讓我吃塊巧克力
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.38,0:17:35.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然春香做什麼都好吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.12,0:17:44.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什麼啊  保坂學長
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.14,0:17:50.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在想什麼時候把這個送給她
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.35,0:17:51.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.49,0:17:58.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用了最高級的比利時巧克力
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.47,0:18:02.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傾盡全力所做的蛋糕
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.23,0:18:05.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…這是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.55,0:18:08.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然是南春香白色情人節的回禮
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.85,0:18:10.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回禮…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.20,0:18:15.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想春香並沒有給保坂學長巧克力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.49,0:18:16.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是當然了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.44,0:18:19.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情人節只有今天而已
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.14,0:18:21.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有計劃隨便行動的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.49,0:18:27.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唔…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.61,0:18:29.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.24,0:18:32.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圭子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.38,0:18:36.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這學校誰最受歡迎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.06,0:18:37.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.19,0:18:41.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石川學長吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.35,0:18:43.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.65,0:18:44.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或許…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.07,0:18:48.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  那傢伙應該還剩很多吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.33,0:18:52.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.67,0:18:54.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉…已經不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.88,0:18:55.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁現在
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.93,0:19:03.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.65,0:19:07.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道藤岡去哪兒了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.14,0:19:10.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他猛地衝出去  四處還巧克力去了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.91,0:19:11.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.87,0:19:13.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是不是討厭吃巧克力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.17,0:19:16.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.40,0:19:24.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把下一節課要用的資料拿來了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.39,0:19:28.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  不是一個班的還要麻煩你  真是謝謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.72,0:19:30.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼  順便而已
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.96,0:19:32.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝啦  這個巧克力拿去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.07,0:19:34.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉…我就不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.22,0:19:36.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的也給你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.24,0:19:36.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.37,0:19:38.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收下吧  來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.16,0:19:42.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…好  真是謝謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.77,0:19:45.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋  你不給他巧克力嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.48,0:19:46.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.31,0:19:47.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉？不是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.64,0:19:48.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不明擺著嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.12,0:20:02.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收到的全都還回去了…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.61,0:20:05.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可最後也沒收到南同學的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.05,0:20:07.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤岡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.40,0:20:09.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.73,0:20:20.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼  一臉兩手空空的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.56,0:20:24.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這兒有很多哦  分一點兒給不受歡迎的你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.43,0:20:27.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…嗯！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.80,0:20:30.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.82,0:20:42.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來  我給你們兩個的情人節禮物
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.14,0:20:45.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太棒了～
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.58,0:20:49.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊～謝謝你  春香姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.32,0:20:54.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  千秋你到底送給誰了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.48,0:21:00.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請收下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.99,0:21:02.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉？給我？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.49,0:21:07.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.90,0:21:09.41,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(春香姐姐  謝謝你)
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.76,0:21:11.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你  千秋
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.56,0:21:16.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  希望有一天你不是給我而是給真正喜歡的對象
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.25,0:21:20.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…對春香姐姐是一心一意的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.14,0:21:22.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說  我的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.58,0:21:39.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃掉簡直太浪費了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.22,0:21:44.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊  那就由我來…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.69,0:21:47.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊！！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.50,0:21:49.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做什麼啊  你這傢伙！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.72,0:21:56.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我吃膩這又黑又甜的東西了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.75,0:21:58.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你給我舔鹽去吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.37,0:22:00.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別…別這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.77,0:22:20.77,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}心の奥集めた　今日の光を持って
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.77,0:22:20.77,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}懷揣著內心深處收集好了的今天的希望
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.42,0:22:29.56,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}飛び込んだ未知の先　何が待ってるのかな
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.42,0:22:29.56,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}躍入未知的前方　那裡有什麼正等待著我們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.85,0:22:38.90,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}未来への共鳴　想い出に重ねれば
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.85,0:22:38.90,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}若是與未來共鳴　不斷憶起今天的希望
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.10,0:22:47.94,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}勇気になる　強さになる　一人じゃないから
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.10,0:22:47.94,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}就會生出勇氣　就能變得堅強　也就不再是獨自一人了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.13,0:22:50.25,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}（聴かせて）
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.13,0:22:50.25,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}（讓你傾聽）
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.34,0:22:58.87,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}明日もきっと会えるね　本当の笑顔で行こう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.34,0:22:58.87,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}明天也一定會與你相遇　我會帶著真誠的笑容前去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.06,0:23:07.75,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}夢見る夜明けを　一緒に迎えたい
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.06,0:23:07.75,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}好想和你一起迎接夢想中的黎明
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.92,0:23:16.93,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}無限の時間よりも　瞬間を駆け抜けよう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.92,0:23:16.93,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}與其坐擁這無限的時刻　倒不如追趕那絢爛的瞬間
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.18,0:23:28.13,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)}その夢の声いつか聴かせてね　信じてく
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.18,0:23:28.13,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)}相信我　總有一天會讓你傾聽那夢中的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.59,0:23:34.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道笊籬蕎麥和蒸籠蕎麥的區別嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.73,0:23:36.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據說是過去用的蘸汁不同
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.05,0:23:38.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笊籬蕎麥用的首鍋湯汁
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.38,0:23:40.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒸籠蕎麥則用再煎熬的湯汁
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.41,0:23:43.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在就只知道加紫菜的是笊籬蕎麥了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.42,0:23:46.22,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\an8\fad(370,0)}第8碗  「游泳池是同父異母的姐妹」
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.67,0:23:45.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊～突然想吃蕎麥麵了
